{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fa5e14c6f0483ab95ff5e1f0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "多列布局声明提供了一种多列组织内容的方式，正如你在一些报纸中看到的那样。这篇文章介绍怎么使用这一特性。",
        "text_hash": "7b29cd047f9d800415d245f77113aaecd2ff147afbccdac39e4a9403a04ef3ce",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4f2b1b6ce9ebd2f7381113b4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "前提：",
        "text_hash": "60df7f5b49d0fd69c1a1ee4bda41ede8b786ae9d162b8a9a73e264bbf703119b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cecdf24d20302028c2ffca8c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "HTML 基础 (study\n         Introduction to HTML ), 和了解 CSS 如何工作的 (study\n         Introduction to CSS .)",
        "text_hash": "a6bc26ac79b4914dbb215c7c86230da611e3355dd49e2479765e2fd328f3ebbb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_06ba40811b10ddb84ef41c54",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "目标：",
        "text_hash": "4d2d25a2888d3e7c13db6b2e275e0179ab434807992666123db412d5f31e27a0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6494f1d23a891e77731e9cba",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "掌握在 web 页面中创建多列布局的方法？，正如你在一些报纸中看到的那样。",
        "text_hash": "2a13cc2e0df38316dce19cd40524ca3fe3c13017589f3d9130397cfe35c9b3c8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7759ab8e870a94cd31964680",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一个简单的例子",
        "text_hash": "d6b26a4bca9cc3f77e620b2d2b085c857674f964038d19dcdf21b36fe21cd3c6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cd92f48523d32fb90df1451f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们将学习怎么使用多列布局，通常也简写为 _multicol_。你可以从这里开始 downloading the multicol starting point file 然后在合适的地方加入 CSS。在这一小节的结尾，你可以看到最终代码的效果。",
        "text_hash": "fbd948b1684f772b1df44e36d80312bd4f02d2a78f8ebd99394d4ecbf5e2933b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_60e8ce09ac00ef28a334ac8f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "三列布局",
        "text_hash": "6fbfdced341f07b20a9b895a7d9e925f462cc14707846c6319443907552223ad",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8683601cbfa258b107e4bad1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们从一些很简单的 HTML 开始；用带有类 container 的简单包装，里面是标题和一些段落。",
        "text_hash": "2c194767d95e26bf2c37bcc26fec574f654583c19ebc33433ffe367cb212aa0c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_281d78d002dad4230f5b4463",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "带有 .container 的  将成为我们 multicol 的容器。通过这两个属性开启 multicol  或者 。 column-count 将创建指定数量的列，所以如果你把下面的 CSS 加到样式表里让后重载入页面，你将得到 3 列：",
        "text_hash": "6feb797d5f8a46c3c5d52e8acad9b4fb87565b07ff2c17bb6feac5972939f9d9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_370de74f43fb2666dbbecec2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n.container {\n  column-count: 3;\n}",
        "text_hash": "db55bd7d399828aa3b86743a2cf86193405ff251791284dd26e041288cbb6a71",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3c057338bfcf78d5daf6656f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "创建的这些列具有弹性的宽度 — 由浏览器计算出每一列分配多少空间。",
        "text_hash": "3c25086e82ab174db9b84e9bbf014fab4dbf4f4babc125e5f7ac74ad7e89a391",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a12d059ca977881e7dfc3202",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css hidden\nbody {\n  width: 90%;\n  max-width: 900px;\n  margin: 2em auto;\n  font:\n    0.9em/1.2 Arial,\n    Helvetica,\n    sans-serif;\n}",
        "text_hash": "8d462692de0256a7f6b32392215400e12922bdf4da2a5dc155f9f9636aa40623",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
