    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_673b2b18142b7fb5102050e9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Multicol 创建的列无法单独的设定样式。不存在让单独某一列比其他列更大的方法，同样无法为某一特定的列设置独特的背景色、文本颜色。你有两个机会改变列的样式：",
        "text_hash": "ec0de08ddb226e57c55ed73e71c089e651846d527325073d83f5c091c802dd7c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d3a636ae53b720cc134fe9d8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "使用  改变列间间隙。\n用  在列间加入一条分割线。",
        "text_hash": "494b03031a7de3ba909589c8739dc2b76db93bfe9fd98f63d14a2eefa0544f61",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2cc502367b861ea89a026548",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "以上面的代码为例，增加 column-gap 属性可以更改列间间隙。",
        "text_hash": "913310e9b58a773e9ef7533a4ab4a1b9531b2f778cee5533619ceb017eb00bd6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cb4e4c70ba22562e140920ba",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "你可以尝试不同的值 — 该属性接受任何长度单位。现在再加入 column-rule。和你之前遇到的  属性类似， column-rule 是  和 的缩写，接受同 border 一样的单位。",
        "text_hash": "f4e247f34d23ebacd7278b484cda4879640e6554e275a771c44237022b147b98",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f4ddbbc95e8f918eda746619",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n.container {\n  column-count: 3;\n  column-gap: 20px;\n  column-rule: 4px dotted rgb(79, 185, 227);\n}",
        "text_hash": "32bd6bbebfa621b513d0849f78b21987caea4c2e8e18d43598895e9c201f2cdc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
