    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_387c873c77822384b1364460",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "值得一提的是这条分割线本身并不占用宽度。它置于用 column-gap 创建的间隙内。如果需要更多空间，你需要增加 column-gap 的值。",
        "text_hash": "e3c3dc6ec98995cd1f50228308c6b23850bacdbe04f0560fdd0059fd212fdfff",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e66db0af2b5d9d5f378b60df",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "列与内容折断",
        "text_hash": "b827c18966fd9fe8c8f6aa14bf104c71eae8f97e89e245e9d66a5f3317e1367b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b49152cecd63174252900813"
      },
